# init(from:)

**Initializer**

Creates a data-value dictionary from another dictionary.

## Declaration

```swift
init?(from dataValue: MLDataValue)
```

## Discussion

Use this initializer to create an [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/DictionaryType] from another data-value dictionary instance. You can confirm the data value’s underlying type by retrieving a non-`nil` value from [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/dictionaryValue] or by inspecting the [doc://com.apple.createml/documentation/CreateML/MLDataValue/type] property.
